INSTALLATION UNDER UBUNTU LINUX

# apt-get install liblexical-persistence-perl libterm-readline-gnu-perl libnet-ssh2-perl

COMMON TO ALL OPERATING SYSTEM

$ mkdir ~/metabrik
$ svn co http://svn.metabrik.org:81/core/tags/METABRIK_1_00 ~/metabrik/core
$ svn co http://svn.metabrik.org:81/repository/trunk ~/metabrik/repository

$ export PATH=$PATH:~/metabrik/core/bin
$ export PERL_RL=Gnu

$ metabrik

Enjoy.
